'''Akarere ka Çamlıdere''' (soma «camlidere»; izina mu [[giturukiya]] : ''Çamlıdere ilçesi'' ) ni akarere kari mu [[Intara y’Ankara|ntara y’Ankara]] y’igihugu cya [[Turukiya]]. Akarere ka Çamlıdere ni kamwe mu turere 16 tugize Intara y’Ankara. Akarere gatuwe n’abaturage bagera kuri Akarere ka [[Beypazarı]]  (abagabo 4.944 n’abagore 4.918)<ref>[http://report.tuik.gov.tr/reports/rwservlet?adnksdb2=&report=idari_yapi_2008.RDF&p_il1=6&p_yil=2008&desformat=html&ENVID=adnksdb2Env  TÜİK]</ref> , batuye kubuso bwa km² 632,63 .

== Izina ==
Iryo zina ryakomotse ku magambo 2 yo m’ururimi rw’igiturukiya ariyo («'''çamlı'''» '[[Umubunda (pinusi)|umubunda]]' na «'''dere'''» 'umugezi').

